  <h2>The Challenge:</h2>
  <div class="side-by-side">
    <p>
      1. Differentiate Code Freedom from other esports circuits with a unique,
      exciting brand presence that would resonate with FPS and Battle Royale
      audiences.
    </p>
    <p>
      2. Create scalable assets that could be easily adapted for multiple
      tournament cycles and marketing campaigns, but stay within the US Army's
      strict brand guidelines.
    </p>
    <p>
      3. Appeal to hardcore competitors and casual viewers alike, ensuring
      maximum brand visibility through the life of the campaign.
    </p>
  </div>
