      <p class="big">Big Reveals for a Big Franchise</p>
  
      <p>
        My team developed the emblem-like Code Freedom logo in collaboration with
        the Army National Guard, exemplifying the brand's best qualities with an
        esports flair. Following a grand reveal of the new logo in cinematic
        fashion, I directed a video for each event in the series, bringing a unique
        style to each entry, and ensuring each reveal trailer felt new and exciting.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="big">Non-Stop Entertainment</p>
      <p>
        We leaned hard into making Code Freedom an absolute beast of an entertainment experience, with non-stop broadcasts that kept fans engaged with the action over 250,000+ minutes of viewer watch time. With unique branding for each event, an analyst desk segment that avoided having BRB screens altogether, and plenty of shoutouts and CTAs for the Guard, our team and the ARNG squad alike were blown away by our creative direction over this six-event series.
      </p>
